{"type":"message","id":"d5c0aa1f","parentId":"81ac501c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T19:11:37.419Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-21 03:11 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下道简网络相关行业的最新动态：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n请搜索最新资讯（2025年底至2026年初），整理3-5条关键信息，输出结构化的学习笔记内容。"}],"timestamp":1774033897411}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc7d85fe","parentId":"d5c0aa1f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T19:11:42.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to search for the latest industry news related to 道简网络's business areas:\n1. Enterprise digital transformation\n2. Smart security\n3. Network system integration\n4. IT operations services\n\nI need to search for latest information from late 2025 to early 2026 and compile 3-5 key pieces of information into structured study notes.\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"a0060ddf2239e12d0fc3e5cb99290ad42f01a6b1843e5c6ffb058fdc283faccb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_amkjledz0ugw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":127,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31214,"totalTokens":31458,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001524,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037456799999999995,"total":0.00393318}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774033897416}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae71d6a4","parentId":"bc7d85fe","timestamp":"2026-03-20T19:11:42.352Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_amkjledz0ugw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774033902349}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b192de8","parentId":"ae71d6a4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T19:11:48.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for each of the four topics. Let me run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"bb2a39557f293d041234d7f2de615192bb24767deee4c36c2ff288009ab88122"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwrehjvknc9h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2025年底 2026年初 最新政策动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwrehjvknc9h_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2025年底 2026年初 行业动态 AI赋能\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwrehjvknc9h_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2025年底 2026年初 行业发展趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rwrehjvknc9h_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2025年底 2026年初 AIOps 智能化趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -500","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":884,"output":289,"cacheRead":31089,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32262,"cost":{"input":0.0002652,"output":0.00034679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009326699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0015446699999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774033902352}}
